{"tid":2068954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高院駁回吳重儀唔准小學教師襲警罪成保釋的申請，現可保釋等候上訴","createTime":"2020-06-18T05:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T11:21:36.000Z","uid":230104,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3172213f1f523d130734c412806f43b7be9cc6c6","tid":2068954,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YnCwdJ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYnCwdJ9.png&h=ccbd1940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙灘排球港隊成員兼小學教師楊博文，去年11月11日駕車上班途中遭交通警截查，其間被指提膝撞到警長腹部，早前受審。裁判官吳重儀指現場另外兩名警員供稱看不到楊老師提腳的動作，顯示各警員沒有夾口供，斷言三警誠實可靠，裁定楊老師襲警罪成。裁判官更揚言關注楊的心智還能否教書，將他還押小欖精神病治療中心候判。楊今向高等法院申請保釋，法官潘敏琦聽罷陳詞後，批准楊保釋外出候判。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法官批准被告以2萬元現金、女友的2萬元人事保釋外出，其間不准離港、須交出旅遊證件、居於報住地址，並且每天向警署報到；若精神科專家要跟被告見面，被告須到小欖接受檢驗。"},{"pid":"ef77cbb532592cc49e143495b88d4ba470f70eae","tid":2068954,"uid":230104,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"低級法院果批低級法官應該集體去上法治再培訓課程"},{"pid":"c248455b9c685fea8f4cc32eb1564d4099301742","tid":2068954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b703521952845217d903ef5050e710db7aecb8fe","tid":2068954,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"根本扯貓尾<br />\n受害人已住幾日"},{"pid":"4dc7656ae737884ccd9beb828481c6880070ef85","tid":2068954,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef77cbb532592cc49e143495b88d4ba470f70eae","tid":2068954,"uid":230104,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"低級法院果批低級法官應該集體去上法治再培訓課程"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"去支那上？"},{"pid":"b2c777c291d86a7fa6e08a32a31c82c49e7e387f","tid":2068954,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"法官批准被告以2萬元現金、女友的2萬元人事保釋外出，其間不准離港、須交出旅遊證件、居於報住地址，並且每天向警署報到；若精神科專家要跟被告見面，被告須到小欖接受檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n呢個條件，唔講以為佢係毒犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a7ea9c84940b20cdebc766888e9c8b8d6ac6b2","tid":2068954,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacd87840cb40d6a49ca6386e6b280f3a8c67a4d","tid":2068954,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"d976dcf1bc8fcf05e04cd33617de17882b64dcc3","tid":2068954,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:22:47.000Z","msg":"投訴吳重儀要繼續"},{"pid":"e89f1eeb5a698384a7f2d71bef531db6dee117c1","tid":2068954,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e366facbefcf75c13b38f9bbdff451a75d0012","tid":2068954,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef77cbb532592cc49e143495b88d4ba470f70eae","tid":2068954,"uid":230104,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"低級法院果批低級法官應該集體去上法治再培訓課程"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:31:27.000Z","msg":"上乜鬼<br />\n全部清算"},{"pid":"dd718ce35ad7ad2149bb5b61b1c26ecbc740eb78","tid":2068954,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}